  <steps>
    <Step id="c009b2f4-c3f0-4a68-b81e-9ba442faa8b3" name="Planning Process" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;The purpose of the planning process is to decide what action needs to be undertaken in response to the referral. The planning process will generally result in one of the following actions:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Immediate action is required go straight to investigation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Phone based planning takes place.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Formal planning meeting is organised.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" intro="true">
    </Step>
    <Step id="dce263d3-39e3-4ca2-9391-ef982e73f98a" name="Possible Outcomes of the Planning Process" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;No further safeguarding activity is required&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Emergency intervention is required&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Proceed to investigation&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Proceed to Large Scale Investigation&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;">
    </Step>
    <Step id="a6586f37-79dd-4b80-8087-5b03464494be" name="Investigation" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;If the outcome of the planning process is to proceed with the investigation, the aim of the investigation is to gather evidence to establish if abuse has taken place.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;The aim of the investigation will be to:-&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;Establish matters of fact about one or more incident(s) in which concerns have been raised.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;To assess the support and protection needs of the vulnerable adults.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;To determine how is responsible and/or capable and what action should be recommended in relation to them.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;To review the management of the setting/service and any improvements required or sanctions to be recommended.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;If there are any concerns regarding the vulnerable person's mental capacity, consideration should be given to include an independent mental capacity advocate to the investigation process.&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;">
    </Step>
    <Step id="a118ad88-b589-47c4-bf6c-1636707557ab" name="Case Conference" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color='#000000'&gt;The purpose of the Case Conference is to bring together the vulnerable person, their advocate and carers as appropriate and multi-agency staff who may be responsible for providing services and managing risks. The following people should be invited to attend. Those who are unable to attend must submit a report for consideration - &lt;b&gt;Chair, Lead Investigator, Police, CQC, Minute Taker, Care Provider, Health Rep, Adult at risk&lt;/b&gt; and &lt;b&gt;Family Member.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;">
