    </Step>
    <Step id="9f85ccb9-dad1-40f2-b9d0-55aa55d23410" name="Possible Outcomes from a Case Conference" title="" number="" html="&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;b&gt;No further safeguarding activity is required&lt;/b&gt; - However further care management involvement may be required.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;b&gt;Protection Plan required.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;b&gt;Action required in relation to the perpetrator.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;b&gt;Issues for services involved have been identified&lt;/b&gt; - The case conference should identify the action required, the timescale and who will monitor the action plan.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;b&gt;Issues for commissioning and contracting have been identified&lt;/b&gt; - The conference should identify how the issues will be passed to the commissioning and contracting directorate.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align='left'&gt;&lt;textformat tabstops='[0]' indent='-20' leftmargin='40'&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='16' color=''&gt;•&lt;TAB&gt;&lt;/TAB&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face='Articulate' size='13' color=''&gt;&lt;b&gt;Issues for multi-agency working have been identified&lt;/b&gt; - The conference should agree how these actions will be shared across partner agencies.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/textformat&gt;&lt;/p&gt;">
